content: The app is very nice and useful. However, the only drawback is that it takes a lot of space in the storage and it can not be transfered to the SD card, which limits the ability to install other apps in the device. I hope the developers fix this ASAP. Note that this is the issue for all endless educational apps.
But waiting to download is forever! Wish it would load. It shouldn't take weeks. I now have buyers regret. Thus was pricey for an app.
replyContent: The app must be left open and your device online for the downloads to complete.  Depending on the content upgrade you purchased, the download may take 5-10 minutes to complete.  Also, if you have enabled the screenlock on the device, this may be the problem as downloads will pause whenever the screenlock is active.
